00:23:05,433 --> 00:23:07,268
<i>[hits target]</i>

429
00:23:07,336 --> 00:23:10,305
James Powell: A fine
shot with a parlor pistol.

430
00:23:10,373 --> 00:23:12,273
John Wilkes Booth:
Thank you, Mr. Powell.

431
00:23:12,341 --> 00:23:13,942
James Powell: Payne.

432
00:23:14,010 --> 00:23:15,143
It's Payne.

