00:23:16,946 --> 00:23:20,883
I ain't goin' by
Powell no more.

435
00:23:20,951 --> 00:23:22,651
Abraham Lincoln: Let
us all join in doing

436
00:23:22,719 --> 00:23:24,320
the acts necessary.

