00:23:29,660 --> 00:23:31,127
of the White House.

441
00:23:31,194 --> 00:23:33,328
Booth is there.

442
00:23:33,396 --> 00:23:36,265
Abraham Lincoln: It is
also unsatisfactory to

443
00:23:36,332 --> 00:23:38,767
some that the elective
franchise is not

