758
00:37:59,654 --> 00:38:03,156
telling Noah Brooks that
"a farce, or comedy,

759
00:38:03,223 --> 00:38:05,258
is best played;

760
00:38:05,325 --> 00:38:09,661
a tragedy is best
read at home."

761
00:38:09,729 --> 00:38:11,462
A last-minute meeting
